{"aid": "igkp3hv6ofq4wu", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 4, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "hwfmxxld7w611e", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-15T22:42:01Z", "content": "<p>只有在保护模式下,80386的全部32根地址线有效,可寻址高达4G字节的线性地址空间和物理地址空间,可访问64TB(有<br />2^14个段,每个段最大空间为2^32字节)的逻辑地址空间</p>\n<p>为什么是2^14个段&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": "关于保护模式下逻辑地址空间寻址"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446634948146, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-03-16T00:24:36Z", "id": "i7b4pq0ylxpio", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T10:47:36Z", "content": "<p>保护模式下&#xff0c;段表包括GDT&#xff08;Global Descriptor Table&#xff09;和LDT&#xff08;Local Descriptor Table&#xff09;两张&#xff0c;每一张段表可以包含8192 (2^13)个描述符[1]&#xff0c;因而最多可以同时存在2 * 2^13 = 2^14个段。<br /></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>虽然保护模式下可以有这么多段&#xff0c;逻辑地址空间看起来很大&#xff0c;但实际上段并不能扩展物理地址空间&#xff0c;所谓的64TB逻辑地址空间&#xff0c;很大程度上是相互重叠的&#xff0c;在32位模式下&#xff0c;真正的物理空间仍然只有2^32字节那么大。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Reference</p>\n<p>[1] 3.5.1 Segment Descriptor Tables, Intel® 64 and IA-32 Architectures Software Developer’s Manual</p>", "subject": ""}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T02:37:30Z", "content": "<p>这段话的上下文是在哪一章节&#xff1f; </p>\n<p>请给出网址</p>", "subject": ""}, {"uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T02:34:38Z", "content": "<p>这段话的上下文是在哪一章节&#xff1f; </p>\n<p>请给出网址&#xff01;</p>", "subject": ""}, {"uid": "hdjoucuyb836fq", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-03-16T00:24:36Z", "content": "<p>这段话的上下文是在哪一章节&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hwfmxxld7w611e", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-16T07:09:33Z", "id": "i7bj6hrfl2h19o", "updated": "2015-